---
<section class="cta" id="contact">
  <div class="container-x cta__inner">
    <div class="cta__line reveal"><span class="sec-tag">Онлайн-запись · Yclients</span></div>
    <h2 class="cta__title">
      <span data-tr>Приходите</span>
      <span class="cta__line-italic" data-tr>познакомиться</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="cta__lead reveal">
      Выберите удобное время и&nbsp;мастера — запись подтвердим за&nbsp;5&nbsp;минут.
    </p>
    <div class="cta__actions reveal">
      <span class="magnet">
        <a href="https://b692514.yclients.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--brand" data-hover>
          Записаться онлайн
          <span class="btn__arrow">→</span>
        </a>
      </span>
      <a href="https://t.me/highbrow_msk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cta__tg" data-hover>
        или написать в&nbsp;Telegram
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta {
    padding: 200px 0 160px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cta__inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .cta__line .sec-tag {
    justify-content: center;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .cta__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(56px, 10vw, 160px);
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin: 0 0 40px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .cta__line-italic {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-brand);
  }

  .cta__lead {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(17px, 1.5vw, 20px);
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
  }
  .cta__actions {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 28px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .cta__tg {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--color-muted-2);
    padding-bottom: 3px;
    transition: color 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .cta__tg:hover {
    color: var(--color-brand);
    border-color: var(--color-brand);
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .cta { padding: 110px 0 80px; }
  }
</style>
